Yousra is the featured borrower for Yousra Group. She and other group members requested this Al Majmoua loan because they have always been neighbors and friends. They are working hard to develop their businesses and earn a good living.
Yousra is a 47-year-old married mother of two children who two years ago started selling cosmetics and make-up from her house to help her husband cover the needs and expenses of their family. Yousra is a hard worker who has a good reputation among her customers. She loves her business and she is trying hard to develop it The loan from Kiva's field partner Al Majmoua would increase her business merchandise with a new collection of cosmetics and make-up that suits the spring and summer seasons. Yousra is at the far right in the photo.
